《'''歡迎來到布達佩斯大飯店'''》（{{lang-en|''The Grand Budapest Hotel: Original Soundtrack''}}）是[[布达佩斯大饭店|2014年同名喜劇劇情片]]的原聲帶專輯。它是由{{tsl|en|ABKCO Records|ABKCO唱片}}於2014年3月4日發行。[[亚历山大·德斯普拉|亚历山大·德斯普拉]]是與[[魏斯·安德森|魏斯·安德森]]第三張合作的原聲帶。它是啟發自{{tsl|en|Russian folk music|俄羅斯民謠}}的唱片，當中包含交響樂作曲和周圍環境的{{tsl|en|drone (music)|持續音音樂}}<ref name=Reed2014>{{cite news |last=Reed |first=Ryan |title=Stream Wes Anderson's ''The Grand Budapest Hotel'' Soundtrack |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/stream-wes-andersons-grand-budapest-hotel-soundtrack-20140226 |accessdate=2014-03-30 |newspaper=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |date=2014-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314153208/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/stream-wes-andersons-grand-budapest-hotel-soundtrack-20140226|archive-date=2014-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯中有專業管弦樂隊參與，例如{{tsl|en|Osipov State Russian Folk Orchestra|奧西波夫州俄羅斯民謠管弦樂隊}}以及50位來自法國和俄羅斯的[[巴拉莱卡琴|巴拉莱卡琴]]演奏家所組成的樂團<ref name=indscore>{{cite news |last=Jagernauth |first=Kevin |title= Exclusive: Pics Of Recording Sessions For ‘Grand Budapest Hotel,’ Randall Poster Talks Score, Wes Anderson & More |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2014/06/exclusive-pics-of-recording-sessions-for-grand-budapest-hotel-randall-poster-talks-score-wes-anderson-more-84671/ |accessdate=2020-02-28 |publisher=Indiewire |date=2014-06-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200229004445/https://www.indiewire.com/2014/06/exclusive-pics-of-recording-sessions-for-grand-budapest-hotel-randall-poster-talks-score-wes-anderson-more-84671/ |archive-date=2020-02-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=pitchfork2014>{{cite news |title=Stream Wes Anderson's The Grand Budapest Hotel Soundtrack on Pitchfork Advance |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/54108-stream-wes-andersons-the-grand-budapest-hotel-soundtrack-on-pitchfork-advance/ |accessdate=2014-03-30 |website=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]] |date=2014-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202190038/https://pitchfork.com/news/54108-stream-wes-andersons-the